title: Switch to Previous Tab in Firefox
tags: @zettel _method firefox
roam-id: 8850c6bb-69d2-4c64-b1d3-d8581e73c32f
type: text/markdown

- browse `about:config`
- find `browser.ctrlTab.sortByRecentlyUsed`
- set `true`
- use `Ctrl+Tab`

[source](https://superuser.com/questions/290704/switching-back-to-last-tab-on-firefox)
